THE GAME
--------

  'Pivobar' is a Workbench game where you have to move a coloured
bar from its starting position at the upper left, toward the
'exit' tile, which is represented by a 'pressed down' tile, that
is located at the bottom right of the game board.

  To move the bar, one and only one of the neighbouring tiles must
be aligned with the tile the bar is located on... otherwise, the
tile on which the bar is located will rotate by 90 degrees.

  Complete the game in the least amount of moves...

  Have fun!

